title: Return to Castle Wolfenstein XBOX NTSC
description:
Published by:                      Activision
Developed by:                    Nerve Software
Region:                               NTSC
Genre:                                 First-Person Shooter 
Number of Players:             1-2
Release Date:                     May 6, 2003 
ESRB Content Descriptors: Blood, Gore, Animated Violence

Xbox Live enabled installment in the long-running Castle Wolfenstein first-person shooter franchise. Himmler, the Fuhrer&#039;s bloodthirsty SS chief, has dabbled in the occult to create an army of the undead-and only one man can stop him. You&#039;re B.J. Blazkowicz, a bad-ass Army Ranger recruited into the Office of Secret Actions. Your mission: blast across the globe and into the dark depths of Castle Wolfenstein-battling carcass-shredding mutants and death-wielding zombies-to terminate Himmler&#039;s demonic experiments. Turn the tides of war before it&#039;s too late
